          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As the winter season approaches, golfers need gear that not only looks the part but performs well in the unpredictable elements. The <strong>Nike Winter 24 Golf Collection</strong> on TRENDYGOLF delivers precisely that - combining cutting-edge technology with style to keep golfers playing comfortably and confidently through chilly conditions. This detailed review explores the collection's key offerings, examining how Nike continues to innovate, providing apparel and footwear that meet the modern golfer's needs, both on and off the course.</p>"
