    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Technical Apparel Designed for Versatility and Comfort",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Nike has consistently set the bar high when it comes to technical golf wear, and the Winter 24 collection is no exception. The <strong>Dri-FIT ADV Tour Polo</strong> - a centrepiece of the range - epitomises Nike's focus on combining form and function. Crafted using advanced moisture-wicking technology, this polo keeps players dry, comfortable, and unrestricted. Specially engineered zones provide ventilation in key areas like the back and underarms, ensuring maximum breathability during intense rounds.</p><p>In addition to its performance aspects, the polo's sleek design, available in sophisticated colourways, gives it a versatile appeal that works well beyond the greens. Whether worn tucked or untucked, it transitions effortlessly from the course to the clubhouse, aligning with Nike's goal of creating apparel that merges lifestyle and sport.</p><h4></h4><h4><strong>Mid-Layers and Hybrid Jackets: Essential for Layering</strong></h4><p>For those who play in colder climates, layering is essential, and Nike's mid-layers and hybrid jackets are designed with this in mind. The Winter 24 collection introduces pieces with <strong>Therma-FIT ADV</strong> technology - Nike's advanced fabric that provides lightweight warmth without compromising on flexibility or range of motion. These hybrid jackets feature a blend of wind-resistant and water-repellent materials, making them ideal for wearing as outer layers when temperatures dip.</p><p>The mid-layers, including quilted gilets and thermal tops, can be worn under these jackets for additional insulation. Nike's focus on ergonomic design ensures that these pieces fit well without feeling bulky, allowing golfers to swing freely while staying warm and dry.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
