          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Footwear plays a critical role in performance, and the Nike Winter 24 collection introduces the latest in its <strong>Air Zoom</strong> series. Notable models like the <strong>Air Zoom Victory Tour III NRG</strong> and the <strong>Infinity Tour NXT% II</strong>  GTX are designed specifically for winter conditions. These shoes feature high-traction soles that provide stability on wet and uneven terrain, ensuring a solid foundation for every swing.</p><p>The Air Zoom technology embedded in these shoes offers responsive cushioning, enhancing comfort during long rounds. The shoes are also constructed with waterproof uppers, keeping feet dry even in damp conditions. Moreover, Nike's attention to sustainable design is evident, as the shoes incorporate recycled materials, aligning with the brand's broader environmental initiatives.</p><h4><strong>Style Meets Functionality: The Design Details</strong></h4><p>Nike's winter footwear doesn't just perform well - it looks great too. The collection features various colourways and styles, offering a stylish yet subtle aesthetic that matches various apparel combinations. These designs make the shoes suitable not just for the course but also for casual wear, reflecting Nike's commitment to creating products that transcend traditional boundaries between sportswear and lifestyle fashion.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
