          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golfers who are undeterred by the elements will appreciate Nike's selection of wet weather apparel in the Winter 24 collection. With options like the <strong>Nike Repel Tour Full Zip Jacket</strong> and <strong>Trousers</strong>, players can face the most challenging conditions with confidence. These items use advanced seam-sealing technology to ensure water resistance while remaining lightweight enough for unrestricted movement. The jackets, available in full-zip designs, feature adjustable cuffs and hem drawstrings to customise the fit, providing additional protection against the wind.</p>"
