    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Sustainable Performance: A Commitment to Eco-Friendly Golf Apparel",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Nike's focus on sustainability is a crucial component of the Winter 24 collection. As part of their ongoing Move to Zero campaign, many items in the collection use recycled polyester and other sustainable materials. This approach not only reduces waste but also enhances performance, as these advanced fabrics offer moisture-wicking and insulating properties necessary for winter play. The brand's sustainable ethos is particularly evident in pieces like the <strong>Infinity Tour NXT% II NRG Golf Shoes</strong>, which feature eco-friendly materials without compromising the high-performance golfers expect.</p><p></p><h2><strong>Headwear and Accessories: Functional and Fashion-Forward Choices</strong></h2><p>To complete any golfer's winter wardrobe, Nike offers a range of headwear and accessories tailored for both function and style. The collection includes:</p><ul><li><strong>Caps and Beanies</strong>: Perfect for keeping warmth in during colder rounds. Nike's caps use sweat-wicking bands to manage moisture, while their beanies feature thermal materials to keep players warm without adding unnecessary weight.</li><li><strong>Bucket Hats</strong>: A trend that has seen a resurgence in golf fashion, these hats provide a practical solution for players who need protection from both wind and light rain. They also add a stylish touch to any outfit, making them versatile for wear off the course.</li><li><strong>Golf Gloves</strong>: Designed with enhanced grip technology, Nike's winter gloves help maintain control even in damp conditions. These gloves are lined for warmth, ensuring that cold fingers don't affect grip or performance.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
